lblErrMsgNote

Note: If you choose to set the wait flag, the request is immediately sent to AMMO and the lot will wait in the operation until the request gets approved. In this case the request is disapproved, the lot will wait forever at the operation. If you choose not to set the wait flag, the lot will skip the operation if the request is disapproved or it is not yet approved. In this case the lot will be measured at operation only if request is approved.
